songs.title: Bounce billo
songs.lyrics:
I like the way you move shake that body down to the
Floor
Tenu kewe dassa main kudiye ni meri ae tu
Kadd ke tu dil sade seenay cho ve laigi ae tu
Kasame khudaye billo kudiye qayamat ae tu
Billo de lip gloss ankhiane klash nikov
Diesel di jean paake laayian jutiyan jimmy choo's
Takdi mainu wi roz kardi sanu behosh
Mere tu style de ae aaja cheti sade close

Bounce billo bounce billo bouce all along - 4 times
Bouce all night long ..

Bounce billo bounce billo bouce all night long - 4
Times
Mukhda tera chausa ambh lagdi tu sanu bomb
Mitthi muskaan teri chamkan tere mote dand
Hilda tera ik ik ang dil nu pendi hai thand
Jado chankawe wang ho jawa main mast malang
I like the way you move shake the body down to the
Floor
Tenu kinwe dassa main kudiye ni meri ae tu
Kadd ke tu dil sade seenay cho ve laigi ae tu
Kasame khudaye billo kudiye qayamat ae tu ..

Bounce billo bounce billo bounce all night long - 4
Times
Bum bum bum bum bum bum...bum bum bum bum
Bum bum bum bum bum bum...bum bum bum bum
Bum bum bum bum bum bum...bum bum bum bum
Bum bum bum bum bum bum...bum bum bum bum
.. bounce
All night long ..all night long.. 8 times

Bum bum bum bum bum bum...bum bum bum bum
Bum bum bum bum bum bum...bum bum bum bum
Bum bum bum bum bum bum...bum bum bum bum
Bum bum bum bum bum bum...bum bum bum bum
